high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the white table.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of the bread on the table.
Turn around and head back towards the sink on your left.
Cut the green apple into three pieces in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the stove.
Place the apple in the right pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the apple from the stove.
Turn around and head towards the fridge on your left.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a slice of apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a right to the large white table.
Pick up the knife with a yellow handle in front of the loaf of bread.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your left.
Use the knife to slice the apple inside the sink.
Place the knife to the right of the apple inside the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the back left corner in the sink.
Turn around and hang a right at the wall to reach the stove.
Place the apple slice into the back right pan on top of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the apple slice inside of it from on top of the stove.
Turn around and hang a left at the end of the white table to reach the fridge.
Place the pan on the lower top wire shelf inside the fridge and close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan with an apple slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and face the white table with the knife on it.
Take the knife from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink on your left.
Slice the apple in the sink in front of you.
Cut out a slice from the apple in the sink.
Take the apple slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the stove to your right.
Put the apple slice in the pan on the stove in front of you.
Take the pan with the apple slice off of the stove.
Turn around and face the fridge on your left.
Put the pan with the apple slice in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn and move to the white table with the toaster.
Pick up the sharp knife from the table.
Carry the knife to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Slice the bagel in the sink using the knife.
Place the knife in the sink to the right of the bagel.
Pick up a piece of bagel.
Carry the piece of bagel to stand in front of the stove.
Place the bagel slice in the pan on the right back burner.
Pick up the pan with the bagel in it from the stove.
Carry the pan with the bagel in it to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pan and bagel on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move a piece of bagel in a pan to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn right to face table with toaster on it.
Move to table, pick up knife in front of bread loaf.
Turn around and walk to sink, turn left to face sink.
Slice apple in sink into three pieces.
Place knife in sink standing up next to sliced apple.
Pick up top left third of sliced apple out of sink.
Turn around, move to wall.  Turn left and move to stove.
Place apple slice in pot on the top right burner on the stove top.
Pick up the pot with the apple slice in it.
Turn around, move almost to garbage.  Turn left and move towards the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put pot with apple slice on top shelf, close refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Slice apple, place in pot and put in refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around, take a step, and turn to face the sink on the left.
Cut the apple in the sink into 3 pieces.
Put the knife in the sink to the right of the apple.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn right to face the stove.
Put the piece of apple on the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner containing an apple.
Turn around and walk forward and to the left to face the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with an apple piece in the fridge.
